Title: Lost & Found
Plot: The NCIS team has to babysit a 9-year-old son of a missing man, a survivalist who is somehow connected to a cold case murder. The investigation leads the team into the wilderness, where they discover a shocking truth about the man's past.
GuestStars: Dominic Scott Kay, Brian Dietzen, J.R. Bourne, Chris William Martin, Karis Campbell, Candice Coke
